A vintage 1960s-style illustration of a cozy home office scene where a sleek retro computer terminal displays a warm glowing screen, while multiple translucent ghost-like silhouettes of people appear to float out of the monitor, gathering around a small round coffee table as if in friendly conversation. The color palette features muted teals, warm oranges, and cream tones with subtle paper texture overlay. Desk lamp casting soft pools of light, potted plant in corner, mid-century modern furniture aesthetic throughout.
